<script type="text/javascript">

                function getframeheight(iframe) {

                    if( iframe.contentWindow !== null ) {

                        var iframeheight = iframe.contentWindow.document.body.scrollHeight;

                        if( iframeheight !== 0 && iframeheight > 100 ) {

                            var container = document.getElementById('ad-compare-1');

                            container.height = iframeheight + "px";
                            container.style.height = iframeheight + "px";
                            iframe.height = iframeheight + "px";
                            iframe.style.height = iframeheight + "px";

                            console.log("iframe height::" + iframeheight);

                        }
                    }
                }
                   
            </script>

	@media  only screen and ( min-width: 1025px ) {
		.airport-book-wrap-class, .airport-book-wrap-direction,.airport-book-wrap-travellers,
		.airport-book-wrap-from, .airport-book-wrap-to, .airport-book-wrap-button {
			width: 32%;
		}

		.airport-book-wrap-button {
			margin-left: 10px;
		}

		.airport-book-wrap-check-price {
			width: 100%;
			margin-right: 0!important;
			font-size: 12px;

		}
	}
	@media  only screen and ( min-width: 1660px ) {
		.airport-book-wrap-class, .airport-book-wrap-direction,.airport-book-wrap-travellers,
		.airport-book-wrap-from, .airport-book-wrap-to, .airport-book-wrap-button {
			width: auto;
		}

			margin-left:20px;
		}

		.airport-book-wrap-check-price {
			margin-right: 5px;
			font-size: 14px;

		}
	}

<script async="" src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=UA-38317519-29"></script>
<script>
  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
  gtag('js', new Date());

  gtag('config', 'UA-38317519-29');

var trackOutboundLink = function(url) {
  gtag('event', 'click', {
    'event_category': 'outbound',
    'event_label': url,
    'transport_type': 'beacon',
    'event_callback': function(){document.location = url;}
  });
}
  
</script>
